                                        blockchain networks.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="feature">
                                    <h3>Customization</h3>
                                    <p>
                                        With <a href="https://www.substrate.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--c-cyan)">Substrate</a>,
                                        developers can build
                                        their own
                                        app-specific
                                        blockchain and
                                        connect it to
                                        Kusama.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
